highlights.text: “Cuaderno” by Dalex, Nicky Jam, Justin Quiles, Sech, Lenny Tavárez, Feid, and Rafa Pabön is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 59 spots at #126.
“Never Really Over” by Katy Perry is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #11.
Billie Eilish has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “bad guy” is the highest at #2.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 126 weeks straight.
